=== EVENT_PIRATE_CONVOY ===
# id: 11
# title: Pirate Convoy
# chinese_title: 海盗船队
# category: PirateEncounter
# mode: starmap

A small convoy of pirate ships lumbers through the sector, laden with plunder. Their formation is sloppy — an opportunity, or a lure?

* [Ambush the trailing ship]
  ~ combat_reward(1, 30)
  埋伏 (máifú) — ambush
* [Shadow the convoy to learn their base location]
  ~ gain_item("Hidden Base Coordinates")
  跟踪 (gēnzōng) — follow
* [Avoid them entirely]
  ~ lose_fuel(2)
  避开 (bìkāi) — avoid
